name: Don'tForget
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: don't forget
des: People usually forget their keys, cards, IDs etc. This skill acts as a checklist and will keep a check on what all things you took and what all things you forgot. Just enable it using the phrase Alexa, open don't forget. It provides you with a checklist for all the stuff people usually forget while traveling.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
